headline: Entergy (ETR) Down 3.1% Since Last Earnings Report: Can It Rebound?

headline: Duke Energy invests $600,000 in North Carolina's community colleges to build next generation workforce
summary: Duke Energy Foundation today announced $500,000 to support 19 North Carolina community college programs that are creating a pipeline of skilled workers who will help meet the energy industry's growing workforce needs. A $100,000 grant will also support the Forward Fund to help students in Southeastern North Carolina attain high-wage employment opportunities.
